---
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="relative animate-on-scroll">
        <img 
          src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}designer-photo.jpeg`}
          alt="Designer working in studio" 
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-primary-600 text-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hidden md:block">
          <p class="text-xl font-serif italic">
            "Fashion is the armor to survive everyday life."
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-right">— Bill Cunningham</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-primary-900">Yordan The Designer</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
          With over a decade of experience in costume design for both stage and screen, 
          I blend historical accuracy with creative vision to bring characters to life through fabric and form.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-6">
          My approach combines meticulous research with innovative techniques, 
          working closely with directors, actors, and production teams to ensure each costume 
          not only looks stunning but also serves the narrative and enables authentic performances.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-8">
          Every project begins with deep research into the time period, character psychology, 
          and practical performance needs. I'm passionate about sustainable practices, 
          incorporating vintage materials and environmentally conscious processes whenever possible.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">15+</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Feature Films</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">20+</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Theater Productions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary-600">5</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Award Nominations</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary-600">100+</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Unique Costumes</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>